Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Writing code", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.645342414466423*^9, 
  3.645342416112988*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f6356631-6fe2-4c1e-ac75-\
a559b64cd943"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Tools", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.645342758639546*^9, 
  3.645342759206341*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"13f1eb81-6df4-4390-8516-\
b26977879e2f"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Wolfram Alpha", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.645342761398346*^9, 
  3.645342763062203*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"fda77804-3d54-4315-b53e-\
3300054dbc0e"],

Cell["\<\
You can access Wolfram Alpha by typing a single = at the start of a cell.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.649403930649578*^9, 
  3.649403944328828*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"bcb768c9-3558-47bb-9233-\
e6c6d10f39d5"],

Cell["", "WolframAlphaShort",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.643624908804274*^9},ExpressionUUID->"6ea31e83-2e71-4e6a-8189-\
c54a86cafe63"],

Cell["\<\
Type your query in natural language, and press enter to get a result.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.6494039646330223`*^9, 
  3.6494039766396637`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"5a9cc25e-0530-47ad-a959-\
f07916e935d9"],

Cell["Integrate x^4/2x", "WolframAlphaShort",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.6584704330291243`*^9, 
  3.658470433201084*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f321184c-214d-4676-b88f-\
cec095442c13"],

Cell["There are three things to notice about doing that.", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.6436252845751*^9, 
  3.6436252979817057`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"17a4890e-d04c-4f66-aa1b-\
2a1590a86428"],

Cell["The cell bracket goes black when a cell is evaluating.", "ItemNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.643625302830748*^9, 3.6436253373085403`*^9}, {
  3.649740198454384*^9, 
  3.6497402002139263`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"af4fe771-7fe5-410c-aa43-\
7d9634e6b6ba"],

Cell["\<\
The input cell now has a small In[2] next to it, where the number describes \
which evaluation it was.  \
\>", "ItemNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.643625302830748*^9, 3.6436254260937853`*^9}, {
   3.645874535898377*^9, 3.645874578327159*^9}, 3.649403834863409*^9, {
   3.650104259953923*^9, 
   3.650104282131652*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0ae39c93-92dc-4b5d-8722-\
542b73b5f53a"],

Cell["\<\
There is a clickable line of code under the query that replaces the Alpha \
expression with Wolfram Language code.\
\>", "ItemNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.643625302830748*^9, 3.643625488919517*^9}, {
  3.65010429410406*^9, 
  3.650104326546028*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ab30a112-28e1-4aae-baa9-\
6ea9413043e1"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Breakout rooms", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.810158115552765*^9, 3.8101581221005507`*^9}, 
   3.810158190323921*^9, {3.810158360902912*^9, 
   3.810158363890381*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8ec82355-d781-4951-b47a-\
db8e1e9ad820"],

Cell["\<\
Compare the outputs you obtain using a single = or a double == at the \
beginning of the input line when you ask for the height of Ben Nevis.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.810158135557682*^9, 3.81015818208141*^9}, {
  3.810158221626597*^9, 
  3.8101582216279097`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2106b482-9110-42d5-8124-\
00e34763932f"],

Cell["\<\
Use the single = at the start of a cell to find out what the motto of the \
University of Aberdeen is.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.810158135557682*^9, 3.81015818208141*^9}, {
  3.8101582227534523`*^9, 
  3.8101582562274513`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0b4ae2ca-5057-4c73-b78b-\
ef34985138f3"],

Cell["\<\
Use he single = at the start of a cell to compute the time of your local \
sunrise.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.810158135557682*^9, 3.81015818208141*^9}, {
  3.8101582227534523`*^9, 3.810158255111373*^9}, {3.810158336985753*^9, 
  3.81015836695711*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8b8c188a-3b60-4feb-b07d-\
1eee65626c92"],

Cell["\<\
Use he single = at the start of a cell to compute the seconds left in this \
year.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.810158135557682*^9, 3.81015818208141*^9}, {
  3.8101582227534523`*^9, 3.810158255111373*^9}, {3.810158336985753*^9, 
  3.810158356289341*^9}, {3.810158443714559*^9, 
  3.8101584585585613`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e7e555f6-cddd-4c80-bb2c-\
4a6e3902a15e"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["", "SlideShowNavigationBar",
 CellTags->
  "SlideShowHeader",ExpressionUUID->"dd8a058b-06d5-42fb-9583-fcd40797ca51"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Writing code", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.645342414466423*^9, 
  3.645342416112988*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a94dce2a-7733-4bd5-80bb-\
9c95a5ccacf4"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Tools", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.645342758639546*^9, 
  3.645342759206341*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a850432a-1c61-46cd-aab0-\
9c3089cb2e20"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Code assistant and suggestions bar", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.645342761398346*^9, 3.6453427771897717`*^9}, {
  3.64534320809892*^9, 
  3.6453432133519793`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1911d6dc-048b-4aca-859f-\
caa0f5176e14"],

Cell["\<\
Third, if you know the beginning of the name of the function, there is a code \
assisant for while you are writing commands.  Start typing Plot in a new \
input cell.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.6436237890741158`*^9, 3.64362382620127*^9}, {
  3.645337273420806*^9, 
  3.645337319889991*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"69ddd226-e944-440d-abc9-\
8bfc8fd22c34"],

Cell[BoxData["Plo"], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.643623828356938*^9, 3.643623828639124*^9}, {
  3.645337296407257*^9, 
  3.6453372966592617`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ae2f012f-c40d-42a7-9c93-\
9ebbcfc587e6"],

Cell["\<\
When you type, you will see a popup under your writing suggesting various \
function names.  Either click on one or select it with the arrow keys and \
press enter.  This will complete the full function name.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.643623917254847*^9, 
  3.643623971428377*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a15b76ad-c510-46b6-b3c3-\
d68e48ca7b20"],

Cell["\<\
 The down arrow, or \[CloverLeaf]/\[ControlKey] + \[ShiftKey] + K, can be \
used to insert a function template.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.650104411360269*^9, 3.6501044264940243`*^9}, {
  3.76863421036033*^9, 
  3.768634211250629*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"dffa0f15-1b6a-46be-8fd2-\
043b4749869a"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"Plot3D", "[", 
  RowBox[{
   TagBox[
    FrameBox["f"],
    "Placeholder"], ",", 
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{
     TagBox[
      FrameBox["x"],
      "Placeholder"], ",", 
     TagBox[
      FrameBox[
       SubscriptBox["x", "min"]],
      "Placeholder"], ",", 
