Cell["\<\
There are pages on every function in the language, with interactive examples \
for you to try.  Along the bottom of the home page are some links that will \
lead you to How Tos, Guides and Tutorials.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.644822630298613*^9, 3.644822681120043*^9}, {
